# Day 1: Prompt Engineering

## 🤖 What is Prompt Engineering?
Prompt engineering is the skill of writing clear, well-structured instructions 
for an AI tool so it understands exactly what you want — like giving precise 
directions instead of vague ones.

## 💡 Why It Matters
The same question can get a generic answer or a powerful one — depending 
entirely on how you phrase it. Good prompting = AI becomes a reliable partner, 
not a guessing game.

## ❌ Weak Prompt
> "Write something about marketing."

## ✅ Improved Prompt
> "Write a 100-word LinkedIn post for small business owners explaining why 
> social media consistency matters more than going viral. Use a friendly, 
> confident tone and end with a question."

## ✨ 3 Benefits of Better Prompts
1. **Saves time** — fewer back-and-forth attempts
2. **Improves quality** — sharper, more relevant answers
3. **Builds consistency** — repeatable results across tasks

